snippet.title: The Brantley Method
snippet.description:
This channel is designed as an opportunity to tell the stories of people who Justin has encountered. The foundational pillars for TBM are Inspiration, Motivation and Education; the mission is to utilize these amazing stories as a vehicle to provide all three of those pillars to the world in unique ways. We welcome you to travel with us on this journey, "Subscribe" to stay up to date with our mission, "Comment" to share your feedback about our stories & "Share" with those who you feel could benefit! 🎈

"The highest human act is to inspire..." Nipsey Hussle
